Cookies preferences

To ensure the website works properly, G-Star Raw (and affiliates) always use functional cookies and similar techniques. We may also use cookies to display (personalized) advertisements, to provide social media features and to analyse website traffic. For a complete overview of the cookies we use and the purposes involved, please click here.
In some cases we also share information with our partners about your use of our website. These partners may combine this data with other information you have provided to them or that they have collected based on your use of their services. If you consent, G-Star may show you personalized recommendations and ads which better match your interests. Also in newsletters and notifications if you want to receive those.
You can change the cookie settings at any time via your browser settings. For more information, please visit our cookie statement and our privacy statement.
